          <li><strong>Days 3-7:</strong> Complete every profile field. Add Botox and your injectables as named services with descriptions. Upload 15+ current photos. Add your booking link.</li>
          <li><strong>Days 8-14:</strong> Reply to every existing review. Set up a review request habit: a text with a direct review link sent to every patient after their visit.</li>
          <li><strong>Days 15-21:</strong> Audit your website. Make sure "Botox Miami" and your injectables have a real, dedicated page that loads fast on mobile and has a visible booking button and a 4.7+ review badge above the fold.</li>
          <li><strong>Days 22-30:</strong> Build your first neighborhood page (start with your strongest patient catchment, often Brickell or Coral Gables). Publish your first Google Post. Set a recurring weekly review-request and posting cadence.</li>
        </ol>

