        <h2>Bottom Line</h2>

        <p>"Botox near me" is the most valuable search a Miami med spa can win because the person typing it is ready to book. You will not win it by accident. You win it by getting into the map pack, and you get into the map pack by stacking the two factors you control: relevance (your Google Business Profile, category, and named services) and prominence (a steady flow of 4.7-star reviews and real neighborhood content). Proximity is fixed. Everything else is a decision.</p>

        <p>Most Miami med spas have a half-finished profile and a stale review pile. That is not a problem. It is the opening. Fix the profile this week, build the review habit this month, and start the neighborhood pages. The patients are already searching.</p>

